My first impressions/thoughts on the Dunhill Signature Collection of fragrances that were launched last year. Are you a fan of these four fragrances? Or just not interested? Please let me know, please add a comment below so that I can find out. 

Dunhill Signature Collection Fragrances - FragranceEx $110. 49 on Dunhill: $130

Arabian Desert: Amber, Incense, Saffron, Oud, Night Blooming Jasmine, Rose, Bergamot
-Alexandra Monet

British Leather: Mate, Leather, Vetiver, Black Pepper, Lavender, Orange Blossom, Patchouli
-Pierre Negrin

Indian Sandalwood: Sandalwood, Orris Butter, Patchouli, Carrot, Cypriol
-Carlos Benaim

Moroccan Amber: Amber, Saffron, Coffee Tree, Immortelle, Ginger, Coriander, Hazelnuts
-Gino Percontino
